name: CourseSeeker.com
overview:
CourseSeeker is the leading global training reservation system which enables business professionals to search for training and register on-line through it’s website, www.courseseeker.com. CourseSeeker helps students find the training they need, from the vendor they want, at the most convenient time and location.

As an industry pioneer, CourseSeeker has established the first Global Distribution System (GDS) for the training industry. Our GDS, internet based Computerized Reservation System (CRS), and CRS data feed services allow students to quickly find the training they need while, at the same time, allowing training vendors to achieve maximum visibility with the least amount of effort.

CourseSeeker is a privately owned company headquartered in St. Louis, Missouri, USA.
